data.description: This multi-unit property for sale is located in the Bronzeville neighborhood. It features three units, including a first-floor unit that duplexes down for additional living space, bedroom and bathroom. The property is being sold as is, meaning that any repairs or updates that may be needed will be the responsibility of the buyer. Despite this, the property has a lot of potential and is an excellent opportunity for savvy investors or owner-occupied buyers looking for a multi-unit property. The neighborhood offers easy access to major transportation routes, parks, shops, and restaurants, making it a convenient location for residents.
